interestingcomments.content:
Cleaning /!/ Sent myA7R-II off to someone to get it cleaned. my 35mm Zeiss was dirty and so was my 24-70.

Does anyone have experience with cleaning their Sony camera and lenses? I was in Yellowstone NP and it was dusty as hell. Camera and lenses all got dust inside, making for wonderful floaties in all my photos.
